{"tid":2082833,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"突發：街工唔參選2020立會選舉","createTime":"2020-06-28T10:35:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-28T12:01:03.000Z","uid":323538,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a7d23916acbac93bf470226120358d1c585ce21c","tid":2082833,"uid":323538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T10:35:54.000Z","msg":"屌！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 白頭佬最後可能自己個議辦出黎選！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FaFy4sY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFaFy4sY.jpg&h=87ce409d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【「街工」不參選2020年立法會選舉聲明】<br />\n.<br />\n就「街工」於6月19日宣佈有意參選立法會的記者會上，對泛民主派初選提出應考慮更全面的數據──7月初選加上中期民調，以供參選團隊參考，再作商議決定是否繼續參選或棄保，可惜無論在事前或事後我們的建議均無法得到充分討論，「街工」對此深表惋惜。<br />\n.<br />\n我們曾表明願意參與泛民主派初選，亦就初選建議提出過改善方案，並從沒想過無視民主派於新界西的共同協調，不理會初選結果而自行決定繼續參與選舉。為了表明「街工」並不是戀棧議會席位及保持泛民為爭取更多議席的團結，我們謹在此宣佈，「街工」不參選2020年立法會選舉。<br />\n.<br />\n沒有立法會議席，在社會角色和資源上，無疑對我們的工作有影響，但卻不會動搖我們追求社會公義的意志。我們將本着「街工」三十五年來的精神：「為弱勢出聲、為貧者出力、為勞工出頭、為民主奮鬥」，堅持下去，奮力不懈，繼續為基層勞工維護權益；為社區、為社會作出貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n街坊工友服務處<br />\n2020年6月28日<br />\n<br />\n聯絡人：<br />\n梁靜珊(9220 6326)<br />\n盧藝賢(5465 8238)"},{"pid":"352f3448f52dfa4f17d1175a9850dcd697d3293c","tid":2082833,"uid":323538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T10:36:07.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"f4e597582817d5082e5e1ac64f2e68cdc155eb1d","tid":2082833,"uid":61271,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T10:37:41.000Z","msg":"幾好<br />\n希望大家唔好再屌白頭佬<br />\n集中火力初選打保皇黨"},{"pid":"00aae0003f1691899b4a0c5dcd772dad8b86aaa8","tid":2082833,"uid":335898,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T10:39:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">BIG暈？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"b29059819ca8458f5b45a9337dd9bec185ebe4a8","tid":2082833,"uid":323538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4e597582817d5082e5e1ac64f2e68cdc155eb1d","tid":2082833,"uid":61271,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T10:37:41.000Z","msg":"幾好<br />\n希望大家唔好再屌白頭佬<br />\n集中火力初選打保皇黨"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T10:43:32.000Z","msg":"一日結果未定，一日白頭佬都會出現。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n梁耀忠：有議席o既地方，就有我！</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf7f85f702abe77bb319436286a45c2c890e9ed1","tid":2082833,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T10:46:59.000Z","msg":"好事"},{"pid":"7f244ffb9bf9092738da011932b03bb7bf7b588c","tid":2082833,"uid":323538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T10:55:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a0eb71d19680a31393ff1ac1a9b69c6ecd63986e","tid":2082833,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T10:57:57.000Z","msg":"白頭佬係抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"046e33897573cb209acf9a13623d9893e1cf43c0","tid":2082833,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T11:11:32.000Z","msg":"good 可以唔割了"},{"pid":"e967fc8c7a543aa14f0a119d0634a7bed00e468a","tid":2082833,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T11:17:38.000Z","msg":"白頭佬退黨，然後自己去選"},{"pid":"820231961545ff9768c6cc261e7cc3b7b7d5ca1f","tid":2082833,"uid":323538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T12:01:03.000Z","msg":"推呀"}]}